Notification Daemon Coco Engine/Theme
*************************************

This engine tries to mimic the behavior of NotifyOSD. It is based on the nodoka
engine by Martin Sourada.

LICENSE INFORMATION
===================
This package is licensed under GPLv3+. Read COPYING for more details.

SHORT DESCRIPTION
=================
This package contains the coco engine for the notification daemon theme.

REQUIRES
========
In order to build you need the gtk2 package.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================
./configure --prefix=/usr
make
su
make install

HOW TO ENABLE
=============
Set gconf "/apps/notification-daemon/theme" key to "coco".
